    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been meticulously pampered and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single mark on it and that fresh new-car feel is still totally there. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
