      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a 'garage queen,' preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory paint job protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, showing zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original leather scent; the premium upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships and a spotless undercarriage that has never seen salt or inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key collector-grade vehicle that has been pampered with obsessive attention to detail. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
